# MDC Rule Location

All MDC rules must be created as individual files in the `claude/rules/` directory.

- Each rule gets its own `.mdc` file (e.g., `claude/rules/my-rule.mdc`)
- Never combine multiple rules into a single file
- Never create MDC rules outside of `claude/rules/`
